folder: Hobart Avenue & Middletown Road, Bronx, NY
text:
(1)
Hobart Avenue, at the N.E. corner of Middletown Road, showing an old farmhouse and barns. The view is south toward Middletown Road.

P. L. Sperr

(2)
A view of the house as seen from Middletown Road. Also shown is the rear of Public School No. 71, fronting on Roberts Avenue.

May 13, 1938

P. L. Sperr

(3)
Another view of the rear of Public School 71, looking north along the west side of Jarvis Avenue.

May 13, 1938

P. L. Sperr
